data.description:
Live in one side and lease the second, or buy it as a full investment property.
This duplex has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a wood burning fireplace on both sides A and B. 
Side B also has a huge covered back porch and a 2 car garage.
Many updates. Both sides are leased currently so will need 48 hours notice for all showings.
